pysyte.types.python
===================

Make a method to suppress sys.stdout and/or sys.stderr

    >>> from pysyte.streams import print_out, print_err


Doctest normally shows all streams

    >>> print_out("Hello"); print_err("World")
    Hello
    World

Suppress stderr
    >>> with quietly:
    ...     print_out("Hello"); print_err("World")
    Hello

Suppress stdout
    >>> with Quietly:
    ...     print_out("Hello"); print_err("World")
    World

Suppress both
    >>> with QUIETLY as suppressor:
    ...     print_out("Hello")
    ...     print_err("World")

Suppressed streams were stored in attributes

    >>> assert "Hello" in suppressor.stdout
    >>> assert "World" in suppressor.stderr

